    <item>
      <title>Teaching</title>
      <link>https://meefen.github.io/home/teaching/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Apr 2016 00:00:00 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://meefen.github.io/home/teaching/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I teach the following courses in the Department of Curriculum and Instruction at UMN:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CI 8371: Applied Social Network Analysis in Education&lt;/strong&gt;*&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An introduction to social network analysis for graduate students in education&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://bookdown.org/chen/snaEd/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Spring &amp;lsquo;17&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CI 8134-35: Foundations of Research in Curriculum and Instruction&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A required course for all first year Ph.D. students in my department&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Co-taught with Dr. Mark Vagle (2016-2017) and Dr. Nina Asher (2017-2018)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CI 5371: Learning Analytics: Theory and Practice&lt;/strong&gt;*&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A general survey of the nascent field of learning analytics and its applications in various educational contexts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://colig.github.io/laumn/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Fall &amp;lsquo;18&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/meefen/la-spring16&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Spring &amp;lsquo;16&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/meefen/LA-UMN&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Spring &amp;lsquo;15&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CI 5301: Foundations of Computer Applications for Business and Education&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This course examines the instructional uses of computers and representative business, education, and marketing applications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/meefen/ci5301&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Syllabus&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CI 4331W: Technology and Ethics in Society&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A liberal education theme, writing intensive course &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/meefen/CI4311W/blob/master/CI4311W-Syllabus-2016-Spring.md&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Syllabus&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Course website hosted on Canvas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;*: New courses developed by myself.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
